snippet.title: 1000 Amps Trailer
snippet.description:
Light up the world! As Plug, you must restore the Amp-Tree-System and thwart an enigmatic intruder. Only you have the ability to give power to whatever you touch. Solve puzzles and explore in 1000 Amps!

Now available! http://theoddmanout.net/1000amps/
